{"tid":1394623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有香港網站一齊響應罷工得唔得","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:39:13.000Z","uid":188913,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcc6d9149315134bd7202709b1e08a1df4a30a0","tid":1394623,"uid":188913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"我有個諗法等網上世界一齊響應8月5號罷工 但係唔知點樣接觸同行宣傳開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得2012年嘅時候 幾個大型網站例如係Google、維基、Craigslist等等一齊喺首頁抗議SOPA法案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/8236-protest-bill-of-sopa-well-known-site-discredit-itself-off-21-pictures\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F8236-protest-bill-of-sopa-well-known-site-discredit-itself-off-21-pictures&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIERV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=ed1653d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/8236-protest-bill-of-sopa-well-known-site-discredit-itself-off-21-pictures</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然停更新都係一個方法 但感覺上如果香港嘅網站可以一齊喺呢一日熄燈 全日維修 又或者喺首頁整大字報會有更大嘅效果 更加多人知！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>推俾做緊小編 網站管理員 Blogger 嘅所有人一齊研究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申: 有網站但唔多人睇 無人跟都會照做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c31e85dad6e6a8cfc27962f374a8b2252d3844d","tid":1394623,"uid":188913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"#我會罷工"},{"pid":"7c88b2599d14bc2d25519cb390828438ab33ca1e","tid":1394623,"uid":188913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"#我會罷工"},{"pid":"a123e2a1f1f4b9026548f4f09495faa270a7d5d2","tid":1394623,"uid":47905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyT